PrecisAuthority to enter into (a) the ALEXIS TREATY LAND ENTITLEMENT AGREEMENT with THE ALEXIS INDIAN BAND which provides for the setting apart of not less than 20,824 acres of land in Alberta for the Band and for the payment of compensation in respect of a specific claim arising from Treaty No. 6, and (b) an AGREEMENT with the Province of ALBERTA respecting the transfer of the subject lands to the Government of Canada.
